msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:269
msgid "在 AgentSociety 2 中的落点"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:270
msgid "ReAct / 语言智能体工具循环"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:271
msgid "推理与外部行动交替，行动用于查询环境、更新事实、处理异常。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:272
msgid ""
"``PersonAgent`` 的 ``ToolDecision`` 循环，以及 ``observation`` / ``plan`` 对 "
"``codegen`` 的调用。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:273
msgid "Component Process Model"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:274
msgid "情绪来自对事件的连续 appraisal，包括新颖性、愉悦性、目标相关性、控制感和规范意义。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:275
msgid "``cognition`` 的 appraisal 变量和情绪强度更新。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:276
msgid "Theory of Planned Behavior"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:277
msgid "意图由 attitude、subjective norm、perceived behavioral control 共同预测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:278
msgid "``state/intention.json`` 的候选目标评分字段。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:279
msgid "Dual-process decision making"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:280
msgid "快速自动加工适合熟悉/低风险情境，慢速审慎加工适合新颖/复杂/冲突情境。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:281
msgid "``plan`` 在单步行动与 ``plan_state.json`` 多步计划之间切换。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:282
msgid "Ebbinghaus forgetting curve"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:283
msgid "记忆保留随时间下降，早期遗忘快，后期变慢；指数形式是简单可控的 baseline。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:284
msgid "``memory_maintenance.py`` 的 retention 衰减。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:285
msgid "ACT-R base-level learning"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:286
msgid "记忆可得性与频率、近因和呈现间隔有关，重复呈现按幂律项叠加。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:287
msgid ""
"``memory`` 的 ``_presentations``、``_access_count``、activation 与 retrieval "
"probability。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:291
msgid ""
"这些理论在框架中是“可解释启发式”，不是心理学参数估计器。它们的作用是让仿真行为有连续性、可调性和可复盘性，同时把 LLM "
"的自由生成限制在可检查的状态文件与工具结果中。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:295
msgid "SkillRegistry API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:297
msgid "``SkillRegistry`` 是技能的发现、管理与执行中心。每个 ``PersonAgent`` 实例持有独立的 registry 副本。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:300
msgid "发现与扫描"
